{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_01",
  "title": "Episode 2 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さーーーーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-saaaaaan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "いつも芽衣達を見ててくれて、ありがとーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for always watching over us～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え？　カメラに近い？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Too close to the camera?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも気持ちを伝えるならこれくらい近い方が伝わるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you’re conveying your feelings‚ it’ll get across better if you’re this close～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9000681471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだ！　芽衣のお母さんからも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! I also have",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "メッセージを預かってるんだ～。読むね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "a message from Mei’s mom～! I’ll read it～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1826529867,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9220.4070133
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5437.347013300002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5917.347013300003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えっと～、ここをこうして～、あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see～‚ I do this here～‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "こうか！　それじゃあ、読むね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like this! Alright‚ I’ll read it～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「芽衣がいつもお世話になっております。実家に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Thank you for always taking care of Mei. Every time she comes back to her parents’ house‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "帰ってくるたび、楽しい話を聞かせてもらっています」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "she tells us fun stories.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9773920998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「騒がしい娘で恐縮ですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“She’s a noisy daughter‚ so I apologize‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "これからもよろしくお願いします」だって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but please take care of her from now on too.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ウエディングドレスの写真を送ってから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since I sent you the wedding dress photo‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのことよく聞かれるんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get asked a lot about {user}-san～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……って、あれ？　カメラ切り替わっちゃってた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? The camera switched!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ずっとすずにゃんが映ってたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ Suzunyān was being filmed the whole time～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、それとウエディングドレスといえば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ and speaking of wedding dresses‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時も誓ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I swore it back then too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大好きだよ、これからもずーっと一緒にいようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love you! Let’s be together forever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "……？　あ、これみんなには内緒だったんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? Ah‚ this was a secret from everyone‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9841177305,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6382.550970699996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと芽衣！　今のはどういうことですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ Mei! What do you mean by that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8560001373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "何か芽衣とよからぬことをしたようですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you did something suspicious with Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0893334706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "芽衣に聞いても、内緒内緒と言うだけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I asked Mei‚ she just said it was a secret",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0032335281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "教えてくれませんし。一体なんなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and wouldn’t tell me. What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.522666804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まぁ、それは今度じっくりと聞かせてもらうとして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’ll hear about that in detail later…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2747754414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれですわよね。感謝というか、お礼というか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that’s right. Gratitude‚ or rather‚ thanks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4844126064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ま、まぁ、私も感謝していないことはないんですのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ it’s not that I’m not grateful?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1940497715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣とのわんにゃんツインズの時も、いろいろと、その",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With the puppy and kitty twins with Mei‚ in various ways‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.922666804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "気持ちを真っ直ぐに伝えられたのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to convey my feelings directly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1252059299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "多少は助けがあったから、なのかなと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "because of the help I received‚ I guess…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2560001373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いろいろと勘違いはありましたが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although there were a lot of misunderstandings‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0257728892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ポテトチップスのCMも、出れて嬉しかったのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was happy to be able to appear in the potato chip commercial.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7560001373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "つ、つまり、何が言いたいのかというと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-so‚ what I’m trying to say is――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3151152609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん、大好き！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I love you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8300345896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
